<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1952-01-23T19:21:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1952-01-23T19:21:00-05:00" n="323" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d323">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">320/1–2352: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the United States Representative at the United Nations</hi>
                                (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Austin</hi></persName>)<note n="1" xml:id="d323fn1">Repeated for information to Rome as
                                3347.</note>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left">
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                                <lb/>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">priority</hi>
                            </seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1952-01-23T19:21:00-05:00">January
                                    23, 1952—7:21 p.m.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>
                            <gloss target="#t_Gadel2">Gadel</gloss> 812. For Gross from Hickerson.
                            Re Membership: Appreciate your <gloss target="#t_Delga1">Delga</gloss>
                            1148 explaining developments Ital membership case. You may be sure your
                            action completely in accord with instructions pursuant <gloss target="#t_Gadel2">Gadel</gloss> 755 and we continue maintain policy
                            set forth therein. <gloss target="#t_Dept1">Dept</gloss> rptd <gloss target="#t_Gadel2">Gadel</gloss> 755 to Rome Jan 18 so <gloss target="#t_Emb1">Emb</gloss> wld be completely informed our
                            position. [Hickerson.]</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>